title: BRIEF-Ikang Healthcare Group Q3 Revenue Rises 33.5 Pct To $206.4 Mln
text: March 22, 2018 / 9:38 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Ikang Healthcare Group Q3 Revenue Rises 33.5 Pct To $206.4 Mln Reuters Staff   Ikang Healthcare Group Inc: * IKANG ANNOUNCES UNAUDITED FINANCIAL RESULTS FOR THE FISCAL THIRD QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 * Q3 REVENUE ROSE 33.5 PERCENT TO $206.4 MILLION * SEES FY 2017 REVENUE RMB 3.57 BILLION TO RMB 3.72 BILLION * QTRLY DILUTED INCOME PER ADS ATTRIBUTABLE TO COMMON SHAREHOLDERS $0.39 * QTRLY NON-GAAP DILUTED INCOME PER ADS ATTRIBUTABLE TO COMMON SHAREHOLDERS $0.40 * IKANG HEALTHCARE - ‍FOR FISCAL YEAR 2017 ENDING MARCH 31,2018, CO REAFFIRMS GUIDANCE OF NET REVENUE TO BE BETWEEN RMB3.57 BILLION AND RMB3.72 BILLION​ Source text for Eikon:
